text: Tracie Spencer (born July 12, 1976 in Waterloo, Iowa) is an American R&B; and pop singer. She has had several hit singles. Her singles are This House, Hide & Seek and Tender Kisses. Her first album, Tracie Spencer, was in 1988. Her second album Make the Difference was in 1990.
